@node ARPIX "Argothian Pixies"

@{b}Argothian Pixies@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = AQ(C4) / (CR(C3)
Type    = Summon Faeries (2/1)
Cost    = 1G
Artist  = Amy Weber
    
Text(CR): Cannot be blocked by artifact creatures. Any damage dealt to
          Argothian Pixies by artifact creatures is reduced to 0.

Text(AQ): Cannot be blocked by artifact creatures. Any damage Argothian
          Pixies take from artifact creatures is reduced to 0.

Flavor Text: @{i}After the rape of Argoth Forest during the rule of the
             artificers, the Pixies of Argoth bent their magic to
             more practical ends.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

