@node CRUMB "Crumble"

@{b}Crumble@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = AQ(C4) / RV(U) / 4E(U) / 5E(U)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = G
Artist  = Jesper Myrfors

Text(5E): Bury target artifact. That artifact's controller gains an amount
          of life equal to its total casting cost.

Text(4E): Bury target artifact. Artifact's controller gains life equal to
          the artifact's casting cost.

Text(RV): Buries target artifact. Artifact's controller gains life points
          equal to target artifact's casting cost.

Text(AQ): Destroy target artifact; artifact creatures may notregenerate.
          Artifact's controller gains life points equal to target
          artifact's casting cost.

Flavor Text: @{i}The spirits of Argoth grant new life to those who
             repent the folly of enslaving their labors to devices.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/CRUMB}

